    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "## Check Your User Concerns and Issues\r\n\r\nUse this AI chat space to check your understanding of user concerns and get feedback on your ideas for fixing them. The goal is to think through how your solutions would affect a real user.\r\n\r\n<br/> \r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n**Step 1:** Choose Files\r\n\r\nFrom the library, upload **the app you analyzed** and let the AI chat know **which user** you want to focus on.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n**Step 2**: Describe The Issues\r\n\r\nThink about what this user cares about, and explain how the issue affects them.\r\n\r\nIn the chat, briefly explain:\r\n- What problem or vulnerability you identified from the user empathy map(s)\r\n- Ideas you have to improve the issue(s)\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n\r\n**Step 3:** Ask for Feedback\r\n\r\nChat with the AI to help you think more deeply about how your solution affects the user’s experience.\r\n\r\n::: details [Pick a question below to test your solutions to the identified issues]\r\n- How would this user react to this solution?\r\n- How does my solution change how this user shares personal info?\r\n- How does my solution make this feature more secure or trustworthy?\r\n- Does it make the app more or less usable for the user?\r\n- What if the solution didn't work as expected?\r\n:::\r\n\r\n",
    "submittable": "false",
